%F A138187 a(n) = 2*floor(n/3) + 1 if (n mod 3) = 0, -4*(floor(n/3) + 1) if (n mod 3) = 1 and 2*floor(n/3) + 3 if (n mod 3) = 2. - _G. C. Greubel_, Jun 16 2021
